ABOUT THE DATA¶

The dataset consists of the daily weather summaries at various weather stations around the world during the World War 2 (WW2) between the years 1940 and 1945.

Metrics¶

In [ ]:
from sklearn.metrics import mean_squared_error, r2_score


def all_metrics(y_test, y_pred):
    mse = mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred)
    report = f"""
    R2 Score: {r2_score(y_test,y_pred):.3f}
    MSE: {mse:.3f}
    RMSE: {np.sqrt(mse):.3f}
    """

    return report
